text: Öråns SK is a sports club in the town of Lycksele in Sweden. It was established in 1970, The club won the Swedish national women's team table tennis championship during the season of 1998-1999. ==References== Category:Table tennis clubs in Sweden Category:Floorball clubs in Sweden Category:Ski clubs in Sweden Category:Athletics clubs in Sweden Category:1970 establishments in Sweden
